value.0: A slab of meat on a rack.
A slab of meat on a rack.

This effigy to Helm seems displaced - it barely fits in the house, and seems somewhat out of place. Still, there is a prayer mat and several candles that denote this as an active place to worship Helm.

This old oil painting depicts a man with noble bearing and a clear mixture of Tethyrian and Calishite heritage. A gold plaque at the bottom of the painting declares the man: "Lord Tiberius Arundel - 1020 DR."
A beautiful rug is in the process of being woven on this loom.

A plain cot with a few old blankets tosses on it as a makeshift mattress and another rolled up as a pillow, doesn't seem that inviting, Yet it's better than sleeping on the floor and allows one a fairly decent nights rest.

A plain cot with a few old blankets tosses on it as a makeshift mattress and another rolled up as a pillow, doesn't seem that inviting, Yet it's better than sleeping on the floor and allows one a fairly decent nights rest.

Tough hemp fibers are woven together to form a rough, yet rollable mattress.  Often place on the ground to keep the moisture from seeping through.  They usually have a worn, old woolen blanket rolled up inside  to use as a pillow or a cover.  Little comfort is achieved when resting on it, but keeps the user dry and warm enough to get a few hours of sleep and is often preferred to sleeping on the bare ground.

Smooth and exotic silk sheets line this mattress which is stuffed with some material that feels as if your sleeping on a cloud. Top qualty wool and cotton comforters, washed to a point that they feel extremely soft, with satiny smooth pillows for a perfect head rest, complete this package. Resting here would be akin to a blessing from the gods.
